    "en": {
      "title": "Foreign travel ban for 5 activists",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Magistrate's Court has imposed a foreign travel ban on 5 activists who were at the forefront of protests in the past.",
        "Joseph Stalin (Teachers' Union), Father Jeevanta Peiris, Lahiru Weerasekhara (Youth for Change), Vasantha Mudalike (IUSF), Eranga Gunasekara (SYU) have been banned from traveling abroad by the court."
      ],
